\begin_layout Title
Basic plan for research of two-wire transmission lines.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Authors:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Gianfranco Scordino
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Aleksei Ponomarenko-Timofeev
\end_layout

\begin_layout Author
\begin_inset Newpage newpage
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Below we provide basic layout of what our research will include, what tests
 will be performed to figure out how parameters of transmission line affect
 on characteristics like
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
While studying the parameters of twisted pair we will vary number of twists
 per meter and type of shielding (UTP,FTP).
 We will also consider how the characteristics of the line change if we
 bend it.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
All in all, the full list of our tests is provided below:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Two-wire ribbon line:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Determine how thickness of the applied insulator affects parameters.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Twisted pair:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Determine how the number of twists per meter affects line parameters.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Perform tests with various conditions (wet insulator, temperature change).
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Shielded pair:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Determine how choice of shielding material affects protection from stray
 magnetic fields.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Air coaxial line:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Determine how geometry parameters affect line parameters (a,b).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Determine how washer material selection affects line parameters.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Flexible coaxial line:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Determine how geometry parameters affect line parameters (a,b).
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Two-wire open line:
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Determine how distance between conductors affects parameters of the line.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Calculate radiation losses and cross-talk of the line (how line is affected
 by noise).
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Standard
P.S.: Common test for all lines is how the choice of insulator (gas for air
 coaxial line) affects line parameters.
\end_layout

